Enduaata e Daniel tembata olkeju le Tigris


1  Ore to lari li okuni le Sairos olaiguanani le Parsia nebolokini ororei Daniel, ilo oji enkarna Belteshasa. Naa kesipa apa ilo rorei, naa olarrabal kitok. Nesipu ninye ilo rorei netum eyiolounoto e ina duaata.


2  Ore apa te nena olong'i, naishirita nanu Daniel too wikii uni. Eitu nanu ainos ndaiki sidain, neitu ejing nkiri aashu enaisho oo sabibu enkutuk ai, 
3  neitu nanu aitasim aela te ilata te nena wikii uni naalulung'a. 
4  Ore te nkolong e tikitam oong'uan olapa le dukuya aitashe nanu te ngilata e ilo keju kitok, aa taa, Tigris, 
5   naraposhu nanu nkonyek aainei aing'orisho, naa ng'ura, oltung'ani oishopo too nkilani naapuyiapui, laa keena empolos enye te sahabu e Ufas. 
6  Neikununo osesen lenye anaa osoit oji beril, neikununo enkomom enye anaa enkiwuang'ata, neikununo nkonyek enyena anaa ilkilang'eta ooyupuyup, neikununo nkaik enyena o nkejek enyena anaa enkitiil o suyai osika, ore oltoilo loo rorei lenyena neikununo anaa oltoilo lo lorora. 
7  Ore nanu Daniel aa nanu ake, nadol ina duaata, amu ore lelo tung'ana apa ootii te nebo nanu eitu edol ina duaata. 
8  Neaku aatung'uayioki aa nanu ake nadol ina duaata kitok, nemeetae engolon natelekua ti atua nanu; ore emua o sesen lai neibelekenya oleng, nashalu oleng. 
9  Naitoki nanu aning oltoilo loo rorei lenyena; ore ake pee aning oltoilo loo rorei lenyena, nabatata nanu te nkomom too njo kumok naitabaiki nanu enkomom ai enkop.


10  Naa ng'ura, aaibung'a nanu enkaina naaikirikirie nanu nkaik aainei o nkung. 
11  Naajoki ninye nanu, “Oo Daniel lo tung'ani onyorri oleng, toning'o kulo rorei laajoki nanu, nintashe too nkejek amu ore taata aairriwuaki nanu enitii.” Ore ina kata aaliki ninye ele rorei, naitashe nanu aikirikira. 
12  Naaitoki ninye ajoki nanu, “Miureisho iyie Daniel, amu ore ebaiki ina olong apa e dukuya nitipika ndamunot inono ijo pee ining'u nintobor kewan te dukuya Enkai ino, etoning'oki irorei linono, naewuo nanu te nkaraki e lelo rorei linono. 
13  Ore olkitok le nkitoria e Parsia aaibooyie nanu nkolong'i tikitam o obo; kake aaweuo Mikael aretu, ilo obo kitok loo lkituaak, neaku atung'uayie nanu ninye te ine te nebo ilo kitok le nkitoriae Parsia, 
14  naaewuo nanu aitayiolo ina nayooki adoiki iltung'ana linono too nkolong'i e siadi. Amu ore ina duaata naa enoo nkolong'i e siadi.”


15  Ore pee aaidip ninye airorie nanu te risioroto e kulo rorei, naibelekenya nanu aing'orie enkomom ai enkop neaku mairo. 
16  Naa ng'ura, ore obo onyaanyukie nkerai e tung'ana naaiseyie enkutuk ai, nabol enkutuk ai airo. Najoki nanu ilo oitasho te dukuya nanu, “Olaitoriani lai, ore te nkaraki ina duaata aatijing'a nanu emion, nemeekure aata engolon. 
17  Kaji eiko osinka lo Laitoriani lai te neirorie Olaitoriani lai? Amu meekure taata aata engolon nemetii enkiyang'et atua nanu.”


18  Naaitoki aiseyie nanu obo oata empukunoto e tung'ani naaitagol nanu. 
19  Nejo ninye, “Lotung'ani ele onyorri oleng, miureishoyu, metaa eseriani te nebo iyie; tagolo nintagol oshoke.” Ore ake pee aairorie nanu nagolu najo, “Nchoo Olaitoriani lai eiro, amu kintagolo iyie nanu.” 
20  Neitoki ninye ajo, “Amaa, iyiolo iyie ajo kainyoo pee aewuo enitii? Kake karrinyo taata nanu alo aarare ilo kitok le nkitoria e Parsia; ore pee aidip ataarare ninye, neeitu olkitok loo Lyunani. 
21  Kake kaaliki nanu iyie ina natisiraki ti atua ina buku oosipat; meetae likae laaretu nanu aarare kulo meteleku Mikael ake ilo kitok linyi.

